 ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">{{CLIENTE.EMAIL}}</span></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em><strong>Aos cuidados de: &nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">{{CLIENTE.RESPONSAVEL}}</span></em></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Conte&uacute;do:</span></strong></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>1.0&nbsp;</strong>APRESENTA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>2.0&nbsp;</strong>CONSIDERA&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES T&Eacute;CNICAS</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>3.0&nbsp;</strong>ESCOPO DOS SERVI&Ccedil;OS OR&Ccedil;ADOS</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">4.0&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">DOCUMENTA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O A SER FORNECIDA</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>5.0&nbsp;</strong>CONDI&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES COMERCIAIS</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Atenciosamente,</span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>{{ENGENHEIRO.NOME}}</strong></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>CREA {{ENGENHEIRO.CREA}}</strong></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235); font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:medium\">{{QUEBRA-PAGINA}}</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>1.0 APRESENTA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Apresentamos nossa proposta comercial para o fornecimento de&nbsp;<strong>Relat&oacute;rio Semestral&nbsp;</strong>do Sistema de Prote&ccedil;&atilde;o contra Descargas Atmosf&eacute;ricas (SPDA), conforme determina&ccedil;&otilde;es da portaria N&deg; 598 de Minist&eacute;rio do Trabalho e Emprego, de 07 de dezembro de 2004, publicada no Di&aacute;rio Oficial da Uni&atilde;o de 08 de Dezembro de 2004, que altera a norma regulamentadora de n&uacute;mero 10 (NR10) e tamb&eacute;m norma NBR 5.419/18.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>2.0 CONSIDERA&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES T&Eacute;CNICAS</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">A cada 50 mortes por raios no mundo, uma&nbsp;&eacute; no Brasil, o pa&iacute;s campe&atilde;o mundial em incid&ecirc;ncia do fen&ocirc;meno. S&atilde;o 130 mortes, mais de 200 feridos anualmente e preju&iacute;zos anuais da ordem de um bilh&atilde;o de reais no pa&iacute;s. Desde modo, existe a necessidade de um sistema de SPDA que esteja de acordo com o que institui a norma, protegendo assim a estrutura da empresa e as pessoas que nela est&atilde;o.</span></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Al&eacute;m da seguran&ccedil;a das pessoas e do patrim&ocirc;nio, tamb&eacute;m &eacute; fundamental a regulariza&ccedil;&atilde;o para atender a lei municipal e, caso haja sinistros, estar de acordo com a norma da ABNT NBR 5.419 e com a documenta&ccedil;&atilde;o arquivada no prontu&aacute;rio da empresa para a apresenta&ccedil;&atilde;o &agrave; seguradora e &agrave; defesa&nbsp; civil.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">&Eacute; importante alertar que toda e qualquer proposta de instala&ccedil;&atilde;o de sistema de preven&ccedil;&atilde;o contra descarga atmosf&eacute;rica,&nbsp;<strong>DEVE SEMPRE</strong>&nbsp;atender tecnicamente a NBR 5.419 com sua &uacute;ltima atualiza&ccedil;&atilde;o em 2015.</span></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Nossos servi&ccedil;os s&atilde;o sempre executados de acordo com as seguintes normas:</span></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><big><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>NR 10 -&nbsp;</strong>Seguran&ccedil;a em Instala&ccedil;&otilde;es e Servi&ccedil;os em Eletricidade</span></big></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><big><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>NBR 5.419/2015 -&nbsp;</strong>Prote&ccedil;&atilde;o de edifica&ccedil;&otilde;es contra descargas atmosf&eacute;ricas</span></big></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><big><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>NBR 5.410/2008 -&nbsp;</strong>Execu&ccedil;&atilde;o de instala&ccedil;&otilde;es el&eacute;tricas de baixa tens&atilde;o</span></big></small></span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>Cursos de Especializa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos nossos Colaboradores</strong></span></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Dispomos de uma equipe de colaboradores que possuem os seguintes cursos:</span></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>NR&nbsp;10:&nbsp;Servi&ccedil;os em Eletricidade</strong></span></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Norma Regulamentadora emitida pelo Minist&eacute;rio do Trabalho e Emprego do Brasil que tem por objetivo garantir a seguran&ccedil;a e a sa&uacute;de dos trabalhadores que interagem com instala&ccedil;&otilde;es e servi&ccedil;os em eletricidade.</span></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>NR&nbsp;35:&nbsp;Trabalho em Altura</strong></span></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Estabelece os requisitos m&iacute;nimos e as medidas de prote&ccedil;&atilde;o para o trabalho em altura, como o planejamento, a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o e a execu&ccedil;&atilde;o, a fim de garantir a seguran&ccedil;a e a sa&uacute;de dos trabalhadores com atividades executadas acima de dois metros do n&iacute;vel inferior, onde haja risco de queda.</span></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/captura-da-copia.png\" style=\"font-size:11px; height:150px; line-height:1.6em; width:300px\" /></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235); color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">{{QUEBRA-PAGINA}}</span></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>3.0&nbsp;ESCOPO DOS SERVI&Ccedil;OS OR&Ccedil;ADOS</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">{{PROPOSTA.TIPO_SERVICO}}</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Visita t&eacute;cnica;</em></span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Inspe&ccedil;&atilde;o nas conex&otilde;es existentes;</em></span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Inspe&ccedil;&atilde;o geral do&nbsp;subsistema&nbsp;de capta&ccedil;&atilde;o superior;</em></span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Inspe&ccedil;&atilde;o geral do subsistema de descida&nbsp;e suas interliga&ccedil;&otilde;es;</em></span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n