er: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em><strong>Aos cuidados de: &nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">{{CLIENTE.RESPONSAVEL}}</span></em></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Conte&uacute;do:</span></strong></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>1.0&nbsp;</strong>APRESENTA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>2.0&nbsp;</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:14px\">CONSIDERA&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES&nbsp;T&Eacute;CNICAS</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>3.0&nbsp;</strong>ESCOPO DOS&nbsp;SERVI&Ccedil;OS&nbsp;OR&Ccedil;ADOS</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>4.0&nbsp;</strong>CONDI&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES&nbsp;COMERCIAIS</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Atenciosamente,</span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>{{ENGENHEIRO.NOME}}</strong></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong>CREA&nbsp;{{ENGENHEIRO.CREA}}</strong></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235); font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:medium\">{{QUEBRA-PAGINA}}</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>1.0&nbsp;APRESENTA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Apresentamos nossa proposta comercial para o fornecimento de&nbsp;<strong>Laudo&nbsp;</strong>do Sistema de Prote&ccedil;&atilde;o contra Descargas Atmosf&eacute;ricas (SPDA), conforme determina&ccedil;&otilde;es da portaria N&deg; 598 de Minist&eacute;rio do Trabalho e Emprego, de 07 de dezembro de 2004, publicada no Di&aacute;rio Oficial da Uni&atilde;o de 08 de Dezembro de 2004, que altera a norma&nbsp;regulamentadora&nbsp;de n&uacute;mero 10 (NR10) e tamb&eacute;m norma&nbsp;NBR&nbsp;5.419/18.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>2.0&nbsp;CONSIDERA&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES&nbsp;T&Eacute;CNICAS</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">A cada 50 mortes por raios no mundo, uma&nbsp;&eacute; no Brasil, o pa&iacute;s campe&atilde;o mundial em incid&ecirc;ncia do fen&ocirc;meno. S&atilde;o 130 mortes, mais de 200 feridos anualmente e preju&iacute;zos anuais da ordem de um bilh&atilde;o de reais no pa&iacute;s. Desde modo, existe a necessidade de um sistema de&nbsp;SPDA&nbsp;que esteja de acordo com o que institui a norma, protegendo assim a estrutura da empresa e as pessoas que nela est&atilde;o.</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Al&eacute;m da seguran&ccedil;a das pessoas e do patrim&ocirc;nio, tamb&eacute;m &eacute; fundamental a regulariza&ccedil;&atilde;o para atender a lei municipal e, caso haja sinistros, estar de acordo com a norma da&nbsp;ABNT&nbsp;NBR&nbsp;5.419 e com a documenta&ccedil;&atilde;o arquivada no prontu&aacute;rio da empresa para a apresenta&ccedil;&atilde;o &agrave; seguradora e &agrave; defesa&nbsp; civil.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">&Eacute; importante alertar que toda e qualquer proposta de instala&ccedil;&atilde;o de sistema de preven&ccedil;&atilde;o contra descarga atmosf&eacute;rica,&nbsp;<strong>DEVE SEMPRE</strong>&nbsp;atender tecnicamente a&nbsp;NBR&nbsp;5.419 com sua &uacute;ltima atualiza&ccedil;&atilde;o em 2015.</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Nossos servi&ccedil;os s&atilde;o sempre executados de acordo com as seguintes normas:</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>NR 10 -&nbsp;</strong>Seguran&ccedil;a em Instala&ccedil;&otilde;es e Servi&ccedil;os em Eletricidade</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>NBR&nbsp;5.419/2015 -&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Prote&ccedil;&atilde;o de edifica&ccedil;&otilde;es contra descargas atmosf&eacute;ricas</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>NBR&nbsp;5.410/2008 -&nbsp;</strong>Execu&ccedil;&atilde;o de instala&ccedil;&otilde;es el&eacute;tricas de baixa tens&atilde;o</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Cursos de Especializa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos nossos Colaboradores</strong></span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Dispomos de uma equipe de colaboradores que possuem os seguintes cursos:</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>NR&nbsp;10:&nbsp;Servi&ccedil;os em Eletricidade</strong></span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Norma&nbsp;Regulamentadora&nbsp;emitida pelo Minist&eacute;rio do Trabalho e Emprego do Brasil que tem por objetivo garantir a seguran&ccedil;a e a sa&uacute;de dos trabalhadores que&nbsp;interagem&nbsp;com instala&ccedil;&otilde;es e servi&ccedil;os em eletricidade.</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>NR&nbsp;35:&nbsp;Trabalho em Altura</strong></span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">Estabelece os requisitos m&iacute;nimos e as medidas de prote&ccedil;&atilde;o para o trabalho em altura, como o planejamento, a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o e a execu&ccedil;&atilde;o, a fim de garantir a seguran&ccedil;a e a sa&uacute;de dos trabalhadores com atividades executadas acima de dois metros do n&iacute;vel inferior, onde haja risco de queda.</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/captura-da-copia.png\" style=\"font-size:11px; height:150px; line-height:1.6em; width:300px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:medium\">{{QUEBRA-PAGINA}}</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>3.0&nbsp;ESCOPO DOS&nbsp;SERVI&Ccedil;OS&nbsp;OR&Ccedil;ADOS</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">{{PROPOSTA.TIPO_SERVICO}}</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Visita t&eacute;cnica;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Inspe&ccedil;&atilde;o nas conex&otilde;es existentes;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Inspe&ccedil;&atilde;o geral do&nbsp;subsistema&nbsp;de capta&ccedil;&atilde;o superior;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Inspe&ccedil;&atilde;o geral do subsistema de descida&nbsp;e suas interliga&ccedil;&otilde;es;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><em>Inspe&ccedil;&atilde;o geral do subsistema de&nbsp;aterramento;</em></span></small></big></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Medi&ccedil;&atilde;o da resist&ecirc;ncia&nbsp;&ocirc;hmica&nbsp;de cada ponto de descida;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Descri&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;&nbsp;dos pontos que n&atilde;o atendem a&nbsp;NBR&nbsp;5.419, apontando as solu&ccedil;&otilde;es para elimina&ccedil;&atilde;o do problema, quando necess&aacute;rio;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o dos componentes do&nbsp;SPDA;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Memorial de c&aacute;lculo;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>C&oacute;pia do certificado de&nbsp;calibra&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;do&nbsp;terr&ocirc;metro&nbsp;utilizado para fazer as medi&ccedil;&otilde;es;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Emiss&atilde;o do certificado de t&eacute;rmino e conclus&atilde;o do laudo;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\">Emiss&atilde;o de&nbsp;ART&nbsp;(Anota&ccedil;&atilde;o de Responsabilidade T&eacute;cnica) com a descri&ccedil;&atilde;o de todas as&nbsp;&aacute;reas&nbsp;trabalhadas;</span></span></em></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Certificado de Prote&ccedil;&atilde;o;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><em>Laudo&nbsp;SPDA;</em></span></small></big></span></span></strong></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Registro com fotos dos elementos do&nbsp;SPDA,&nbsp;da Instala&ccedil;&atilde;o e considera&ccedil;&otilde;es t&eacute;cnicas pertinentes;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Para que o LAUDO de&nbsp;SPDA&nbsp;seja v&aacute;lido e aceito pelas autoridades competentes &eacute; necess&aacute;rio que a empresa emissora do documento esteja devidamente regularizada, tendo um engenheiro respons&aacute;vel;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Todos os encargos sociais trabalhistas, impostos e taxas federais, estaduais e municipais pertinentes a&nbsp;PREVETEC&nbsp;devidamente quitadas.</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Ap&oacute;s a aprova&ccedil;&atilde;o do cliente, os colaboradores juntamente ao engenheiro respons&aacute;vel&nbsp;&nbsp;da&nbsp;Prevetec&nbsp;executa a an&aacute;lise &nbsp;total da edifica&ccedil;&atilde;o.</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Caso haja a exig&ecirc;ncia, pelo contratante, do uso&nbsp;plataforma&nbsp;elevat&oacute;ria ou andaime, a mesma n&atilde;o est&aacute;&nbsp;&nbsp;inclusa&nbsp;&nbsp;nesta proposta.</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>A&nbsp;Prevetec&nbsp;segue rigorosamente as normas da seguran&ccedil;a do trabalho.</em></span></span></small></big></span></strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:medium\">{{QUEBRA-PAGINA}}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>4.0&nbsp;CONDI&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES&nbsp;COMERCIAS:</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Custo do LAUDO de&nbsp;SPDA</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Valor:&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">R$<span style=\"font-size:18px\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">{{PROPOSTA.VALOR}}</span></span></strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:medium\">{{PROPOSTA.CONDICAO_PAGTO}}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:medium\">{{QUEBRA-PAGINA}}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>GAIOLA&nbsp;FARADAY&nbsp;/ &nbsp;ESTRUTURAL</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/foto-estrutura-gaiola.png\" style=\"height:250px; text-align:justify; width:600px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>TRABALHAMOS COM GRANDES EMPRESAS A&nbsp;N&Iacute;VEL&nbsp;NACIONAL</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/nova-foto-clientes.png\" style=\"height:381px; width:581px\" /></strong></p>\r\n', 1);
