ze:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Descri&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;&nbsp;dos pontos que n&atilde;o atendem a&nbsp;NBR&nbsp;5.419, apontando as solu&ccedil;&otilde;es para elimina&ccedil;&atilde;o do problema, quando necess&aacute;rio;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o dos componentes do&nbsp;SPDA;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Memorial de c&aacute;lculo;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>C&oacute;pia do certificado de&nbsp;calibra&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;do&nbsp;terr&ocirc;metro&nbsp;utilizado para fazer as medi&ccedil;&otilde;es;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><big><small><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em>Emiss&atilde;o do certificado de t&eacute;rmino e conclus&atilde;o do laudo;</em></span></span></small></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><em><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\">Emiss&atilde;o de&nbsp;ART&nbsp;(Anota&ccedil;&atilde;o de Responsabilidade T&eacute;cnica) com a descri&ccedil;&atilde;o de todas as&nbsp;&aacute;reas&nbsp;trabalhadas;</span></span></em><