</small></span></big></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>Cursos de Especializa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos nossos Colaboradores:</strong></span></small></span></big></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Dispomos de uma equipe de colaboradores que possuem os seguintes cursos:</span></small></span></big></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>NR&nbsp;10:&nbsp;Servi&ccedil;os em Eletricidade</strong></span></small></span></big></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Norma&nbsp;Regulamentadora&nbsp;emitida pelo Minist&eacute;rio do Trabalho e Emprego do Brasil que tem por objetivo garantir a seguran&ccedil;a e a sa&uacute;de dos trabalhadores que&nbsp;interagem&nbsp;com instala&ccedil;&otilde;es e servi&ccedil;os em eletricidade.</span></small></span></big></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>NR&nbsp;35:&nbsp;Trabalho em Altura</strong></span></small></span></big></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Estabelece os requisitos m&iacute;nimos e as medidas de prote&ccedil;&atilde;o para o trabalho em altura, como o planejamento, a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o e a execu&ccedil;&atilde;o, a fim de garantir a seguran&ccedil;a e a sa&uacute;de dos trabalhadores com atividades executadas acima de dois metros do n&iacute;vel inferior, onde haja risco de queda.</span></small></span></big></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/captura-da-copia.png\" style=\"font-size:11px; height:150px; line-height:1.6em; width:300px\" /></span><span style=\"font-size:11px\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:medium\">{{QUEBRA-PAGINA}}</span><span style=\"font-size:11px\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>2.0&nbsp;ESCOPO DOS&nbsp;SERVI&Ccedil;OS&nbsp;OR&Ccedil;ADOS</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">{{PROPOSTA.TIPO_SERVICO}}</span></span></small></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Inspe&ccedil;&atilde;o geral em TODOS&nbsp;os quadros e pain&eacute;is el&eacute;tricos do im&oacute;vel&nbsp;a fim de atestar conformidades e/ou&nbsp;inconformidades, como preconiza a Norma&nbsp;Regulamentadora&nbsp;de n&ordm;10 (NR-10);</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Verifica&ccedil;&atilde;o se&nbsp;&aacute;reas&nbsp;de alta tens&atilde;o (quando houver) est&atilde;o devidamente isoladas e com restri&ccedil;&atilde;o de acesso e&nbsp;sinaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Verifica&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;se tomadas e&nbsp;plugs&nbsp;est&atilde;o padronizados e com identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de tens&atilde;o;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Verifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de passagens de fios nas&nbsp;eletrocalhas&nbsp;referente a: estado, quantidade de cabos, acomoda&ccedil;&atilde;o,&nbsp;fechamente&nbsp;de&nbsp;isolamente, etc.;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Conjunto de procedimentos e instru&ccedil;&otilde;es t&eacute;cnicas e administrativas de sa&uacute;de e seguran&ccedil;a nas instala&ccedil;&otilde;es da empresa;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Emiss&atilde;o de Laudo conclusivo,&nbsp;com registro fotogr&aacute;fico, atestando as reais condi&ccedil;&otilde;es das instala&ccedil;&otilde;es el&eacute;tricas presentes no im&oacute;vel, contemplando&nbsp;ART&nbsp;(Anota&ccedil;&atilde;o de Responsabilidade T&eacute;cnica) do profissional respons&aacute;vel,&nbsp;devidamente paga;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><strong>Ser&atilde;o analisados:</strong></small></span></big></span></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Passagem de cabos em canaletas;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">sinaliza&ccedil;&atilde;o;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de circuito;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">travas dos quadros;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">se existe&nbsp;diagrama&nbsp;unifilar&nbsp;internamente do quadro;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">exist&ecirc;ncia de prote&ccedil;&atilde;o das partes&nbsp;energizadas&nbsp;com barreira isolante (acr&iacute;lico);</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">estado dos&nbsp;cabos;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">conex&otilde;es e terminais;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">aterramento;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">continuidade dos equipamentos;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">poss&iacute;veis&nbsp;interferencias;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">adequa&ccedil;&otilde;es necess&aacute;rias;</span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><big><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">layout&nbsp;de procedimentos de opera&ccedil;&atilde;o.&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235); font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:medium\">{{QUEBRA-PAGINA}}</span></span></small></span></big></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"line-height: 20.8px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>3.0&nbsp;CONDI&Ccedil;&Otilde;ES&nbsp;COMERCIAS:</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><strong>Custo do LAUDO de NR10</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Valor:&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">R$<span style=\"font-size:18px\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">{{PROPOSTA.VALOR}}</span></span></strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:medium\">{{PROPOSTA.CONDICAO_PAGTO}}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235); color:rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:trebuchet ms,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:medium\">{{QUEBRA-PAGINA}}</span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>GAIOLA&nbsp;FARADAY&nbsp;/ &nbsp;ESTRUTURAL&nbsp;</strong></span><strong>(SPDA)</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upl