gb(0, 0, 0)\">Aterramento El&eacute;trico.</span></big></span></div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:left\">\r\n	<div><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Projeto SPDA.</span></big></span></div>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>SISTEMAS DO PARA - RAIOS (SPDA)</strong></span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">&Eacute; um sistema de prote&ccedil;&atilde;o contra raios que tem como objetivo escoar para o solo, no caminho mais curto poss&iacute;vel os raios que eventualmente atinjam a edifica&ccedil;&atilde;o onde est&atilde;o instalados, reduzindo assim os riscos de vida e de danos materiais.</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/Captor-Franklin.jpg\" style=\"height:236px; width:177px\" /></span></small></span></span></strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235)\">{{QUEBRA-PAGINA}}</span></span></small></span></span></strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>O que &eacute; medi&ccedil;&atilde;o &ocirc;hmica?</strong></span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/captura-medicao.PNG\" style=\"height:209px; width:279px\" /></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><big><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">A Medi&ccedil;&atilde;o &Ocirc;hmica &eacute; um &iacute;tem muito importante para se atestar se o p&aacute;ra-raios do seu condom&iacute;nio ou empresa est&aacute; atuando. Ter um p&aacute;ra-raios instalado n&atilde;o significa que ele esteja protegendo seu patrim&ocirc;nio contra descargas atmosf&eacute;ricas. &Eacute; atrav&eacute;s da medi&ccedil;&atilde;o &ocirc;hmica, que &eacute; verificada atrav&eacute;s de aparelhos espec&iacute;ficos como o Terr&ocirc;metro, que pode ser verificada a medi&ccedil;&atilde;o &ocirc;hmica, que deve estar dentro da limite aceit&aacute;vel nas normas t&eacute;cnicas, e de seguran&ccedil;a.</span></small></span></span></big></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><big><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Esta norma, em conjunto com a NBR 5.419 exige dos condom&iacute;nios al&eacute;m de diversas a&ccedil;&otilde;es preventivas de seguran&ccedil;a nas instala&ccedil;&otilde;es el&eacute;tricas, a realiza&ccedil;&atilde;o de Laudo de Instala&ccedil;&atilde;o El&eacute;trica e Laudo de Medi&ccedil;&atilde;o &Ocirc;hmica.</span></small></span></span></big></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><big><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">A periodicidade de realiza&ccedil;&atilde;o do Laudo de Medi&ccedil;&atilde;o &Ocirc;hmica &eacute; anual, j&aacute; para o Laudo de Instala&ccedil;&atilde;o El&eacute;trica, a norma n&atilde;o especifica a periodicidade, por&eacute;m os especialistas sugerem que seja realizado a cada dois anos.</span></small></span></span></big></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>Exemplo de edifica&ccedil;&atilde;o com SPDA</strong></span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Segue aqui uma imagem de como seria a estrutura do local ap&oacute;s a instala&ccedil;&atilde;o do SPDA.</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/estrutura-spda.PNG\" style=\"height:196px; width:300px\" /></span></span></small></span><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235)\">{{QUEBRA-PAGINA}}</span></span></small></span></span></strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>Adesivos de Identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o / Validade</strong></span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/19642790_1795258300784399_1228727823022104020_n.jpg\" style=\"height:191px; width:380px\" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/20170612_114845.jpg\" style=\"height:193px; width:108px\" /></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><small><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">A&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size:24px\"><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\">Para-Raios Bras&iacute;lia </span></span></strong>fornece adesivos de identifica&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;e validade&nbsp;para garantir o profissionalismo em nosso trabalho. Mostrando os dados do local&nbsp;e at&eacute; quando ser&aacute; v&aacute;lido aquele sistema, no qual&nbsp;<em>semestralmente