rsos de especializa&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></strong></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/captura-equipe.PNG\" style=\"height:242px; width:391px\" /></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif\"><em><big><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"background-color:#FFD700\">Riscos, conscientiza&ccedil;&atilde;o, ancoragens, linhas de vida e trabalho ascens&atilde;o e dimens&atilde;o vertical, resgate simples, sele&ccedil;&atilde;o de sistema pessoal contra quedas, adequa&ccedil;&atilde;o de t&eacute;cnicas para subida descida, torres ou poste de transmiss&atilde;o, distribui&ccedil;&atilde;o e subesta&ccedil;&atilde;o, deslocamento horizontal e vertical e demonstra&ccedil;&atilde;o de resgate simples.</span></span></big></em></span></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:#000000\">Nossos servi&ccedil;os s&atilde;o sempre executados de acordo com as seguintes normas:</span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>NR 10 -</strong>&nbsp;Seguran&ccedil;a em Instala&ccedil;&otilde;es e Servi&ccedil;os em eletricidade</span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>NBR 5.419/2015 -&nbsp;</strong>Prote&ccedil;&atilde;o contra descargas atmosf&eacute;ricas (SPDA)</span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>NBR 5.410/2008 -&nbsp;</strong>Instala&ccedil;&otilde;es el&eacute;tricas de baixa tens&atilde;o</span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Cursos de Especializa&ccedil;&atilde;o dos nossos Colaboradores</strong></span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:#000000\">Dispomos de uma equipe de colaboradores que possuem os seguintes cursos:</span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>NR&nbsp;10:&nbsp;Servi&ccedil;os em Eletricidade</strong></span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:#000000\">Norma Regulamentadora emitida pelo Minist&eacute;rio do Trabalho e Emprego do Brasil que tem por objetivo garantir a seguran&ccedil;a e a sa&uacute;de dos trabalhadores que interagem com instala&ccedil;&otilde;es e servi&ccedil;os em eletricidade.</span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>NR&nbsp;35:&nbsp;Trabalho em Altura</strong></span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><big><span style=\"color:#000000\">Estabelece os requisitos m&iacute;nimos e as medidas de prote&ccedil;&atilde;o para o trabalho em altura, como o planejamento, a organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o e a execu&ccedil;&atilde;o, a fim de garantir a seguran&ccedil;a e a sa&uacute;de dos trabalhadores com atividades executadas acima de dois metros do n&iacute;vel inferior, onde haja risco de queda.</span></big></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"color:rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(237, 235, 235)\">{{QUEBRA-PAGINA}}</span></span></small></span></span></strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>Nosso Aplicativo</strong></span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Baixe nosso&nbsp;<strong>app PREVETEC</strong></span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/print-app.PNG\" style=\"height:184px; width:109px\" /></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\">Fale com um de nossos Engenheiros pelo nosso chat online direto em nosso site,&nbsp;ou mande um email para n&oacute;s, estamos sempre a disposi&ccedil;&atilde;os.</span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 5px 10px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0)\"><strong>TRABALHAMOS COM EMPRESAS A NIVEL NACIOAL</strong></span></span></small></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><small><span style=\"font-family:arial,helvetica,sans-serif\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://prevetec.com.br/v3/includes/components/ckeditor/kcfinder/upload/images/nova-foto-clientes(1).png\" style=\"height:346px; width:528px\" /></span></small></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', 1);
